                "text": "Three times per day as a standard action, a grioth can unleash a wave of violent psychic energy. Each non\u2011grioth creature within 30 feet takes 2d6 damage and is shaken for 1d4 rounds. A creature that succeeds at a DC 16 Will save takes half damage, negates the shaken condition, and is immune to the same grioth eclipse seer\u2019s mindshock for 24 hours. This is a mind-affecting effect.",
